# =============================================================================
# Docker Build Context Ignore
# =============================================================================
# Placed in services/ because docker-compose.yml sets `context: ./services`
# Reduces build context size and prevents leaking dev artifacts into images.

# Python bytecode & caches
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd
**/.pytest_cache/

# Test artifacts
**/htmlcov/
**/.coverage
**/coverage.xml

# Virtual environments
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/env/

# IDE files
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.swp
**/*.swo

# Git
**/.git/
**/.gitignore

# OS files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Documentation
**/README.md
**/docs/CLAUDE.md
**/docs/AGENTS.md
